race.comment: CROWN ESTATE (6) hit the frame two starts ago at Wauchope but ran below par last time when sixth. Looks well placed so expect a better run this time. THE DEFIANT ONE (3) was well below his best last time but his prior form measures up. The engagement of Chelsea Hillier is a positive move. Likely improver with strong prospects. OUR WARRIOR (4) is a likely improver after finishing fourth when resuming at Port Macquarie. Better for the hitout and is drawn to take much closer order this time. Gets his chance to break a long run of outs. THEDAYTHEMUSICDIED (5) finished third last time over 1000m at Wauchope when resuming from a spell. Fitter for that and is one to watch.
